title: Ethan's Dream
author: PossessedHood416
description:
If there's anything FNaF has taught me, it's to A: Not to stick my head in heavy machinery, and B: Conserve my battery.

Ethan is asleep. Do not wake him up.

The manual can be found in the manuals folder of the game or at ktane.timwi.de.

Contact PossessedHood416 on Discord if there are any bugs.
